  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个GitLab工作流的图，核心是三路分支：develop、staging和main。develop是主开发分支，所有功能先合到这里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "staging",
        "main",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，develop作为mainBranchName。那流程是先初始化develop，然后分出staging，再分出main吗？还是main从staging分出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "staging",
        "main",
        "init",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，develop先有一个初始commit，然后checkout到staging做分支。staging稳定后，从staging再切出main。main只接收经过staging验证的代码。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "staging",
        "main",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我搭建好了基础结构：develop有初始commit，分出了staging，staging再分出main。现在main上有一个commit，develop上有三个连续的commit。接下来怎么处理合流？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "staging",
        "main",
        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "develop的三个commit开发完成后，要先merge到staging做集成测试。测试通过后在staging上打一个hotfix commit，最后把staging整体merge到main发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "staging",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "hotfix",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下细节：staging上的hotfix commit需要标注具体信息吗？比如\"fix(hotfix): repair the DTO\"这种格式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "staging",
        "hotfix",
        "commit",
        "fix"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，就按这个写。另外图标题用\"Gitlab flow\"，要显示分支名和commit标签。",
